               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”
 I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt,
                     Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 4ra-7vb)
 I-2) Introductory
                     exhortation (fols. 7vb-8vc)
 I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wäʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I
                     worship Thee ...” (fols. 8vc-9vc)
 I-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām: 179 miracles (fols.
                     10ra-156vc)
 I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi ... "Does not the man ..." (distributed
                     among the miracles of Mary, fols. 66ra-90vc)
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
